<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body class="bg-light">
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header text-center">
                        <h1>üèÄ <%= title %>
                        </h1>
                        <p class="text-muted mb-0">Discord Bot Management Panel</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="row text-center">
                            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                                <div class="card h-100">
                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <h3>üéÆ EA Sports Sync</h3>
                                        <p>Connect your Madden 26 league to LEAGUEbuddy through the admin panel.</p>
                                        <a href="/admin/sync" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
                                            Admin Sync Panel
                                        </a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                                <div class="card h-100">
                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <h3>üìä Bot Commands</h3>
                                        <p>Use these Discord commands after connecting your league:</p>
                                        <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                            <li><code>/ea status</code></li>
                                            <li><code>/ea sync</code></li>
                                            <li><code>/ea refresh</code></li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="alert alert-info mt-4">
                            <h5>üö® Important Notice</h5>
                            <p class="mb-0">
                                EA has not yet released a companion app for Madden 26. The admin sync panel above
                                is the recommended method to connect your league until EA releases official mobile
                                support.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="text-center mt-4">
                            <h5>Need Help?</h5>
                            <p>
                                <strong>Setup Process:</strong><br>
                                1. Set your console and Madden version<br>
                                2. Connect your EA Sports account<br>
                                3. Select your league from the list<br>
                                4. Use Discord bot commands to sync data
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>